dialog#activity-forest-menu.activity-forest__menu(
  data-forest-menu
  aria-labelledby='activity-forest-menu-title'
)
  .activity-forest__menu-heading
    div
      p.activity-forest__dialog-eyebrow While you are in the forest
      h2#activity-forest-menu-title Forest menu
    button(type='button' data-forest-menu-close aria-label='Close Forest menu') Close
  section.activity-forest__menu-section(aria-labelledby='activity-forest-shape-title')
    h3#activity-forest-shape-title Shape the clearing
    p.activity-forest__menu-note
      | Make reversible changes to the place around your writing.
    .activity-forest__menu-actions
      button(type='button' data-forest-toggle-trail aria-pressed='false') Edit trail
      button(type='button' data-forest-place-marker) Place marker here
  section.activity-forest__menu-section(aria-labelledby='activity-forest-satchel-title')
    h3#activity-forest-satchel-title Satchel
    p.activity-forest__menu-note A few renewable things the forest has offered.
    ul.activity-forest__satchel-list
      li
        canvas.activity-forest__material-icon(
          width='28'
          height='24'
          data-forest-material-icon='fallen-twigs'
          aria-hidden='true'
        )
        span Fallen twigs
        strong(data-forest-material-count='fallen-twigs') 0
      li
        canvas.activity-forest__material-icon(
          width='28'
          height='24'
          data-forest-material-icon='smooth-stones'
          aria-hidden='true'
        )
        span Smooth stones
        strong(data-forest-material-count='smooth-stones') 0
      li
        canvas.activity-forest__material-icon(
          width='28'
          height='24'
          data-forest-material-icon='seed-pods'
          aria-hidden='true'
        )
        span Seed pods
        strong(data-forest-material-count='seed-pods') 0
    p.activity-forest__menu-note
      | These small finds are renewable. Once an offering is complete, the forest can offer another
      | without taking anything from your satchel.
    h3.activity-forest__menu-subheading Make for the clearing
    .activity-forest__build-list
      button(type='button' data-forest-build='trail-sign')
        strong Trail sign
        span 2 twigs · up to 60 characters
      button(type='button' data-forest-build='stone-bench')
        strong Stone bench
        span 2 stones
      button(type='button' data-forest-build='seed-pod-lantern')
        strong Seed-pod lantern
        span 1 twig · 2 seed pods
    .activity-forest__menu-actions.activity-forest__menu-actions--utility
      button(type='button' data-forest-renew-discoveries disabled) 9 discoveries remain
      button(type='button' data-forest-reset-discoveries) Reset satchel and finds
